## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Run all 3 services locally (`python server.py`, `node server.js`, `npm run dev`).
2. Start an interview — verify camera feed appears in the ProctoringPanel as a smooth `<video>` element.
3. Check Express terminal logs to confirm frame POSTs are reaching FastAPI.
4. Test violations: look away, cover camera, have someone else appear — verify alerts still trigger.
5. End the session — verify reports (JSON, CSV, snapshots) are generated correctly.
6. Build Docker image and verify the container starts without `winsound` or `cv2.VideoCapture` crashes.
